dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.genericstructure.generaltemplateclasses.timevalue

Interface ITimeValue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface ITimeValue
extends IEntity
    ITimeValue: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This is used to specify a multidimensional time value based on ASAM CSE codes. It is specified by a code which defined the basis of the time and a scaling factor which finally determines the time value. If for example the cseCode is 100 and the cseCodeFactor is 360, it represents 360 angular degrees. If the cseCode is 0 and the cseCodeFactor is 50 it represents 50 microseconds.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
